### Debt Tracker API — sample requests (VS Code "REST Client" extension)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@access = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refresh = PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register (returns user + tokens)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Ali", "email": "ali@example.com", "password": "secret123" }

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "ali@example.com", "password": "secret123" }

### Refresh tokens
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "{{refresh}}" }

### Current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Create folder
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/folders
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Friends", "color": "#22c55e" }

### List folders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/folders
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Create contact
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Karim", "phone": "+992900000000" }

### List contacts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Create debt (they owe me)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/debts
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "contact_id": "PASTE_CONTACT_ID", "direction": "they_owe_me", "amount": 250, "currency": "USD", "due_date": "2026-07-01", "description": "Lunch loan" }

### List debts (optional filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/debts?status=pending&direction=they_owe_me
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Add a payment to a debt
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/debts/PASTE_DEBT_ID/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 100, "note": "first installment" }

### Dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Logout (revoke refresh token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "{{refresh}}" }
